<p>Hello {{ admin.name }},</p>

{% if demo %}
<p>Welcome to the CSA Admin demo! Your account has been created and you're ready to explore.</p>

<p>Feel free to click around, create members, send invoices. Everything resets weekly, so you can't break anything.</p>

<p>Use your email (<strong>{{ admin.email }}</strong>) to log in.</p>

{% button action_url %}
  Access the demo
{% endbutton %}

<p>If you have any questions or feedback, just reply to this email. I'd love to hear from you!</p>
{% else %}
<p>An admin account for {{ organization.name }} has been created for you, please use your email (<strong>{{ admin.email }}</strong>) to log in.</p>

{% button action_url %}
  Access the admin of {{ organization.name }}
{% endbutton %}
{% endif %}
